OL,3,CJudith Chalmers, host of ITV's Wish
OL,4,CYou Were Here...? has died aged 90
OL,6,FTV presenter Judith Chalmers, best
OL,7,Fknown for hosting ITV's travel show
OL,8,FWish You Were Here...?, has died aged
OL,9,F90.
OL,11,FHer family said in a statement on
OL,12,FFriday that she died peacefully at
OL,13,Fhome on Thursday evening, surrounded
OL,14,Fby her family, after living with
OL,15,FAlzheimer's in her final years.
OL,17,FThey said her health had been
OL,18,Fdeclining for some time and that she
OL,19,Fhad become seriously ill in recent
OL,20,Fweeks, giving the family time to be
OL,21,Ftogether with her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
