OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779570670
OL,3,CJudith Chalmers, host of ITV's Wish
OL,4,CYou Were Here...? has died aged 90
OL,6,FBorn in Gatley, Cheshire, she began
OL,7,Fworking for the BBC at just 13, going
OL,8,Fon to present BBC Radio programmes
OL,9,FFamily Favourites and Woman's Hour in
OL,10,Fthe 1960s.
OL,12,FShe later hosted ITV's daytime
OL,13,Fmagazine show Good Afternoon before
OL,14,Fgoing on to present Wish You Were
OL,15,FHere...?, an ITV series of 30-minute
OL,16,Fshows about travel and holidays, in
OL,17,F1974.
OL,19,FMs Chalmers presented the primetime
OL,20,Fshow until 2003 and was appointed an
OL,21,FOBE in 1994.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
